  "original_ja": {
    "text": "ベクトルa,bのなす角60°, |a|=1, |b|=2。u=xa+b, v=xa-b。x>1でuとvのなす角が30°となるxを求める。(u·v)^2=[A]/[B]|u|^2|v|^2, a·b=[C]。これをxで表すと x^4-[DE]x^2+[FG]=0。変形して (x^2-[H])^2=([I]x)^2。よって x=[J]+√[KL]。",
    "formulas": [],
    "structure": {
      "is_divisibility": false,
      "has_parameter_elimination": true,
      "has_case_split": true,
      "has_integer_constraint": false,
      "algebraic_complexity": 3
    }
  },
  "solution": {
    "outline": [],
    "steps": [
      {
        "idx": 1,
        "description": "角30°より内積公式（平方）",
        "math": "(u\\cdot v)^2=\\cos^2 30^\\circ\\,|u|^2|v|^2=\\frac34|u|^2|v|^2"
      },
      {
        "idx": 2,
        "description": "a·bを計算",
        "math": "a\\cdot b=|a||b|\\cos60^\\circ=1"
      },
      {
        "idx": 3,
        "description": "u·v, |u|^2, |v|^2 をxで表し整理",
        "math": "u\\cdot v=x^2-4,\\ |u|^2=x^2+4+2x,\\ |v|^2=x^2+4-2x"
      },
      {
        "idx": 4,
        "description": "方程式を解いてx>1を満たす解を選択",
        "math": "(x^2-4)^2=\\frac34(x^4+4x^2+16)\\Rightarrow x=3+\\sqrt{13}"
      }
    ],
    "symbolic_steps": []
  },
